* {{ill|Shikoku Railway Company (JR Shikoku)|ja|四国旅客鉄道|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tosan Line|ja|土讃線|qq=draft}} – {{ill|Zentsūji Station|ja|善通寺駅|qq=draft}} (3.6 km)
; **Road**
* Public road: {{ill|Kagawa Prefectural Road 48: Zentsūji Tarima Line|ja|香川県道48号善通寺詫間線}} – Zentsūji Ballpark (0.3 km)
* Expressway: {{ill|Takamatsu Expressway|ja|高松自動車道|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Zentsūji Interchange|ja|善通寺インターチェンジ|qq=draft}} (4.5 km)

